gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"82774709dc829f31ce4729e4e4b9e187a9282711","tid":1463420,"uid":68471,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T14:05:17.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">塞旅客一定要塞如果唔係出機場做咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n塞嘅話，留返一個counter/閘口出黎，放一條極細既路出黎，由佢地排條好長既隊，排都排一兩粒鐘。其他路block Q曬，咁你就人道了，無位比人入了。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n圍師必缺，你唔使塞死，已經塞死。</span>"},{"pid":"3ea0618decb07295cc0dd251f7dc211734f5f4a9","tid":1463420,"uid":202106,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T14:43:40.000Z","msg":"推到有人理<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"39a1af18c25865bf91ae000b895ed1281a744fcd","tid":1463420,"uid":274272,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T20:42:22.000Z","msg":"8月11日銅鑼灣根本超寧靜，好多手足食緊野休息，突然有班人打人，速龍就拉人<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/100022977031618/posts/488583618584202?s=1592281052&amp;sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F100022977031618%2Fposts%2F488583618584202%3Fs%3D1592281052%26sfns%3Dmo&d=2QIn9Yr%2BOYfG2lc2ZV7v%2Bgy1DEY80m5I9K8mtjxpzv8%3D&h=71a12ff3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/100022977031618/posts/488583618584202?s=1592281052&amp;sfns=mo</a><br />\n片中一開波位黑衫，粉紅口罩者好勇武打人及意圖傷害他人身體者請注意<br />\n根據港大學者張達明表示，放蛇時違法同樣有刑責，呢位黑警明顯知法犯法，鄧炳強話放蛇唔做犯法野明顯講大話<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3UEFidv.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3UEFidv.jpg&h=46d3259c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SHAARyz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSHAARyz.jpg&h=892b8b4b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n大頭相，明顯見到喬裝者口罩係包好實唔係醫療用款式同埋有耳機作溝通，點解成面血就睇埋下邊<br />\n<br />\n追蹤一下喬裝示威者的警員全記錄，請留意相中該兩名黑衣男之螢光綠⾊色波鞋，可以看到該⼈人於不同時段之變化，甚⾄不排除⼩隊以波鞋做記號<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AaTKKTT.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAaTKKTT.jpg&h=08f14f4d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n當時在銅鑼灣怡和街，突然聽到有⽩衫打⼈，就⾒到有⼈被制服。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AXzFidX.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAXzFidX.jpg&h=80bfeb1b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n近睇，留意圖左下⾓螢光綠⾊波鞋及留意右邊⿊⾊螢光鞋男子，當時正在「拘捕」⼀一名白衣男<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Ze4YPmh.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZe4YPmh.jpg&h=b0b479fc&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/q0t3f1m.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fq0t3f1m.jpg&h=1d3e899e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/eZZqumr.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FeZZqumr.jpg&h=d4cc8557&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n不久，馬上有示威者與他們發⽣生肢體衝突，左邊白頭盔者為姓蘇爆門牙講對唔住成地血手足（下稱蘇姓男子）<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vk1MdO5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fvk1MdO5.jpg&h=28733290&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n後來速龍趕到，黑⾊螢光鞋男阻⽌蘇姓男子離開，同時請留意他的背包及⼝<br />\n罩，螢光鞋男未有離開<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ogUenHC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FogUenHC.jpg&h=745a14b5&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/n1cSTPo.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fn1cSTPo.jpg&h=bde18a55&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4Xp6dPs.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4Xp6dPs.jpg&h=d859e8cf&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LzR02HS.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLzR02HS.jpg&h=94964016&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n留意左⼿邊男子，從背包口罩可確認該人為⿊⾊色螢光鞋男，未有被拘捕並離去，蘇姓男子被制服<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/100022977031618/posts/488583618584202?s=1592281052&amp;sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F100022977031618%2Fposts%2F488583618584202%3Fs%3D1592281052%26sfns%3Dmo&d=2QIn9Yr%2BOYfG2lc2ZV7v%2Bgy1DEY80m5I9K8mtjxpzv8%3D&h=71a12ff3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/100022977031618/posts/488583618584202?s=1592281052&amp;sfns=mo</a><br />\n影片中0:50可見蘇姓男子被捕經過，有人好大聲講「自己友」，1:05可見黑色螢光鞋男正在拘捕一位黃衫男<br />\n致於另一位螢光鞋黑警？自己睇相<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DqkpKWr.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDqkpKWr.jpg&h=5337b5c3&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MmOnwBu.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMmOnwBu.jpg&h=aa363679&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2n5QFuT.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2n5QFuT.jpg&h=2655ad9e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8vTKKWE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8vTKKWE.jpg&h=0c20aeba&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XjRo0u3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXjRo0u3.jpg&h=bfa92b5a&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZpY6YgO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZpY6YgO.jpg&h=f6c5a936&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/H42PbBU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FH42PbBU.jpg&h=5882ad77&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vFXLuoD.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvFXLuoD.jpg&h=82336939&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n居然被防暴打，之後出示電筒，再有另一防暴到場先放人，懷疑打人條防暴係大陸公安溝通不足<br />\n影片1:02可見他獲悉經過<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/100022977031618/posts/488583618584202?s=1592281052&amp;sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F100022977031618%2Fposts%2F488583618584202%3Fs%3D1592281052%26sfns%3Dmo&d=2QIn9Yr%2BOYfG2lc2ZV7v%2Bgy1DEY80m5I9K8mtjxpzv8%3D&h=71a12ff3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/100022977031618/posts/488583618584202?s=1592281052&amp;sfns=mo</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Pev1NaA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPev1NaA.jpg&h=6da6c647&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n獲悉成面血繼續開工拉人，噤博命想升職呀？螢光鞋男隨後手持警棍，與另⼀戴上安全帽示威裝扮警員⼀一同協助拘捕蘇姓男子，噤多傷口，擔心蘇姓男子被黑警傳染暗病就真<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5XRDPpj.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5XRDPpj.jpg&h=970f2d0d&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/68JbpXM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F68JbpXM.jpg&h=0467443a&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Mf8R9pw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMf8R9pw.jpg&h=fdcce040&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n之後黑色螢光鞋男接手<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uj4mNbu.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fuj4mNbu.jpg&h=95e70209&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6xbPV4U.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6xbPV4U.jpg&h=809ba1f3&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qjcb9p1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fqjcb9p1.jpg&h=6c24f256&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n滿地鮮血<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/skZh4YF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FskZh4YF.jpg&h=46ca9cae&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/p2BPV5r.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fp2BPV5r.jpg&h=42cb4ecd&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Pj2PbDS.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPj2PbDS.jpg&h=4b70c4e1&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DgcznLC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDgcznLC.jpg&h=6df0a565&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5Rh7HLJ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5Rh7HLJ.jpg&h=31843130&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DNb8sct.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDNb8sct.jpg&h=4c8a1577&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/m8uh4Zd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fm8uh4Zd.jpg&h=b7d8b39a&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4v3iPqX.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4v3iPqX.jpg&h=6df429ca&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n其他喬裝示威者黑警相，留意身型係比較健碩，還有包面包得比普通示威者密實及多數戴耳機<br />\n<br />\n最後，祝蘇姓男子平安"},{"pid":"2c4ec0f57fe3d05498f390e3fa299316f07157fc","tid":1463420,"uid":127952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T01:07:02.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"629e46ce6c4bad74c39a882da546dbeb722d5359","tid":1463420,"uid":653,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T06:53:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"83db00d48755e3a5b63e43bffb9ad3bc78d2eb79","tid":1463420,"uid":202106,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"39a1af18c25865bf91ae000b895ed1281a744fcd","tid":1463420,"uid":274272,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T20:42:22.000Z","msg":"8月11日銅鑼灣根本超寧靜，好多手足食緊野休息，突然有班人打人，速龍就拉人<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/100022977031618/posts/488583618584202?s=1592281052&amp;sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F100022977031618%2Fposts%2F488583618584202%3Fs%3D1592281052%26sfns%3Dmo&d=2QIn9Yr%2BOYfG2lc2ZV7v%2Bgy1DEY80m5I9K8mtjxpzv8%3D&h=71a12ff3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/100022977031618/posts/488583618584202?s=1592281052&amp;sfns=mo</a><br />\n片中一開波位黑衫，粉紅口罩者好勇武打人及意圖傷害他人身體者請注意<br />\n根據港大學者張達明表示，放蛇時違法同樣有刑責，呢位黑警明顯知法犯法，鄧炳強話放蛇唔做犯法野明顯講大話<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3UEFidv.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3UEFidv.jpg&h=46d3259c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SHAARyz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSHAARyz.jpg&h=892b8b4b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n大頭相，明顯見到喬裝者口罩係包好實唔係醫療用款式同埋有耳機作溝通，點解成面血就睇埋下邊<br />\n<br />\n追蹤一下喬裝示威者的警員全記錄，請留意相中該兩名黑衣男之螢光綠⾊色波鞋，可以看到該⼈人於不同時段之變化，甚⾄不排除⼩隊以波鞋做記號<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AaTKKTT.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAaTKKTT.jpg&h=08f14f4d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n當時在銅鑼灣怡和街，突然聽到有⽩衫打⼈，就⾒到有⼈被制服。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AXzFidX.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAXzFidX.jpg&h=80bfeb1b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n近睇，留意圖左下⾓螢光綠⾊波鞋及留意右邊⿊⾊螢光鞋男子，當時正在「拘捕」⼀一名白衣男<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Ze4YPmh.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZe4YPmh.jpg&h=b0b479fc&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/q0t3f1m.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fq0t3f1m.jpg&h=1d3e899e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/eZZqumr.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FeZZqumr.jpg&h=d4cc8557&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n不久，馬上有示威者與他們發⽣生肢體衝突，左邊白頭盔者為姓蘇爆門牙講對唔住成地血手足（下稱蘇姓男子）<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vk1MdO5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fvk1MdO5.jpg&h=28733290&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n後來速龍趕到，黑⾊螢光鞋男阻⽌蘇姓男子離開，同時請留意他的背包及⼝<br />\n罩，螢光鞋男未有離開<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ogUenHC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FogUenHC.jpg&h=745a14b5&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/n1cSTPo.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fn1cSTPo.jpg&h=bde18a55&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4Xp6dPs.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4Xp6dPs.jpg&h=d859e8cf&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LzR02HS.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLzR02HS.jpg&h=94964016&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n留意左⼿邊男子，從背包口罩可確認該人為⿊⾊色螢光鞋男，未有被拘捕並離去，蘇姓男子被制服<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/100022977031618/posts/488583618584202?s=1592281052&amp;sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F100022977031618%2Fposts%2F488583618584202%3Fs%3D1592281052%26sfns%3Dmo&d=2QIn9Yr%2BOYfG2lc2ZV7v%2Bgy1DEY80m5I9K8mtjxpzv8%3D&h=71a12ff3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/100022977031618/posts/488583618584202?s=1592281052&amp;sfns=mo</a><br />\n影片中0:50可見蘇姓男子被捕經過，有人好大聲講「自己友」，1:05可見黑色螢光鞋男正在拘捕一位黃衫男<br />\n致於另一位螢光鞋黑警？自己睇相<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DqkpKWr.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDqkpKWr.jpg&h=5337b5c3&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MmOnwBu.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMmOnwBu.jpg&h=aa363679&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2n5QFuT.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2n5QFuT.jpg&h=2655ad9e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8vTKKWE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8vTKKWE.jpg&h=0c20aeba&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XjRo0u3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXjRo0u3.jpg&h=bfa92b5a&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZpY6YgO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZpY6YgO.jpg&h=f6c5a936&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/H42PbBU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FH42PbBU.jpg&h=5882ad77&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vFXLuoD.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvFXLuoD.jpg&h=82336939&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n居然被防暴打，之後出示電筒，再有另一防暴到場先放人，懷疑打人條防暴係大陸公安溝通不足<br />\n影片1:02可見他獲悉經過<br />\n<a hre